---
---

<section id="nosotros" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-header fade-in">
      <span class="header-badge">Por qué elegirnos</span>
      <h2>Líderes en Logística Internacional</h2>
      <p class="header-subtitle">Conectamos Sudamérica con soluciones de transporte confiables, seguras y eficientes</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <!-- Grid de características principales -->
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card fade-in" style="transition-delay: 0.1s">
          <div class="feature-icon-wrapper">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Cobertura de seguro de transporte</h3>
            <p>Aplicamos controles operativos y seguros de carga para respaldar cada operación de transporte.</p>
            <div class="feature-stat">
              <span class="stat-value" style="font-size: 1.1rem; text-transform: uppercase;">Disponible</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Seguro de carga</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card fade-in" style="transition-delay: 0.2s">
          <div class="feature-icon-wrapper">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Puntualidad Comprobada</h3>
            <p>Rutas optimizadas y planificación estratégica que garantizan entregas a tiempo, cada vez.</p>
            <div class="feature-stat">
              <span class="stat-value">95%</span>
              <span class="stat-label">A tiempo</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card fade-in" style="transition-delay: 0.3s">
          <div class="feature-icon-wrapper">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
                <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Rastreo en Tiempo Real</h3>
            <p>Tecnología GPS avanzada que le permite monitorear su carga en cada kilómetro del trayecto.</p>
            <div class="feature-stat">
              <span class="stat-value">24/7</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Monitoreo activo</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card fade-in" style="transition-delay: 0.4s">
          <div class="feature-icon-wrapper">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
                <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
                <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
                <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Alcance Global</h3>
            <p>Equipo profesional con experiencia en transporte terrestre internacional, marítimo y aéreo, conectando Sudamérica con los mercados globales.</p>
            <div class="feature-stat">
              <span class="stat-value">10 +</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Año Experiencia</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Sección de cobertura -->
  <div class="coverage-section-wrapper fade-in">
    <div class="coverage-section">
      <div>
        <div class="coverage-main">
          <div class="coverage-left">
            <div class="coverage-badge">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                <line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/>
                <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Cobertura Regional</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Conectamos 7 Países de Sudamérica</h3>
            <p>Operamos en las principales rutas comerciales del Mercosur con presencia estratégica en cada país.</p>
            
            <div class="coverage-stats-inline">
              <div class="stat-inline">
                <div class="stat-inline-number">10,000+</div>
                <div class="stat-inline-label">Toneladas</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-inline">
                <div class="stat-inline-number">500+</div>
                <div class="stat-inline-label">Clientes</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-inline">
                <div class="stat-inline-number">8</div>
                <div class="stat-inline-label">Países</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <a href="/cotizar" class="btn-primary-cta">
              <span>Solicitar Cotización Gratuita</span>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
                <path d="M7.5 15L12.5 10L7.5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="coverage-right">
            <div class="countries-grid">
              <div class="country-item">
                <span class="country-flag">🇧🇷</span>
                <span class="country-name">Brasil</span>
              </div>
              <div class="country-item">
                <span class="country-flag">🇦🇷</span>
                <span class="country-name">Argentina</span>
              </div>
              <div class="country-item">
                <span class="country-flag">🇨🇱</span>
                <span class="country-name">Chile</span>
              </div>
              <div class="country-item">
                <span class="country-flag">🇵🇪</span>
                <span class="country-name">Perú</span>
              </div>
              <div class="country-item">
                <span class="country-flag">🇵🇾</span>
                <span class="country-name">Paraguay</span>
              </div>
              <div class="country-item">
                <span class="country-flag">🇺🇾</span>
                <span class="country-name">Uruguay</span>
              </div>
              <div class="country-item">
                <span class="country-flag">🇧🇴</span>
                <span class="country-name">Bolivia</span>
              </div>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: white;
    position: relative;
    overflow: visible;
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }

  .about::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 150px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #eff6ff 0%, transparent 100%);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 5rem auto 4rem;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .header-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe 0%, #bfdbfe 100%);
    color: #1e40af;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .about-header h2 {
    font-size: 3.2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .header-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #64748b;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  /* Features Grid */
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(30,58,138,0.08);
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .feature-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2563eb, #3b82f6);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(30,58,138,0.15);
    border-color: rgba(37,99,235,0.2);
  }

  .feature-card:hover::before {
    transform: scaleX(1);
  }

  .feature-icon-wrapper {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe 0%, #bfdbfe 100%);
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #2563eb;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover .feature-icon {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
    color: white;
    transform: scale(1.1) rotate(-5deg);
  }

  .feature-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .feature-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .feature-content p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #64748b;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature-stat {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%);
    border-radius: 50px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.1);
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #2563eb;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #1e40af;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Coverage Section */
  .coverage-section-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .coverage-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #2563eb 100%);
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    color: white;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .coverage-section > div {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .coverage-main {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .coverage-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .coverage-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .coverage-left h3 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .coverage-left p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    opacity: 0.95;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .coverage-stats-inline {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .stat-inline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .stat-inline-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-inline-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .countries-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .country-item {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .country-item:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }

  .country-flag {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .country-name {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .btn-primary-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background: white;
    color: #1e3a8a;
    padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .btn-primary-cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  .btn-primary-cta svg {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary-cta:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  .coverage-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    top: -200px;
    left: -100px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: float 20s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .coverage-section::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    bottom: -150px;
    right: -50px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: float 20s ease-in-out infinite;
    animation-delay: 5s;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1);
    }
    33% {
      transform: translate(30px, -30px) scale(1.1);
    }
    66% {
      transform: translate(-20px, 20px) scale(0.9);
    }
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .coverage-main {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .countries-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }

    .btn-primary-cta {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-header h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }

    .header-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .feature-card {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .coverage-section {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .coverage-left h3 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .coverage-left p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .coverage-stats-inline {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .countries-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .country-flag {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .btn-primary-cta {
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
